The paper deals with analyzing videos and determining actions being performed, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves machine learning algorithms and comparisons between them, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also explores various datasets available for the problem, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper mentions the possibility of generalizing the task to animals or robots, which falls under robotics (cs.RO).
